snippet.textDisplay: Listen... everyone is upset over the fact the car was detailed then trashed like it was. I used to do car detailing and it did suck knowing the cars you were putting so much work into were just gonna be trashed again (like a farm truck that was going right back to the farm). But as time went on, it really doesn’t matter because at the end of the day you were getting paid decent money just to clean a car. The fact that the guys at car throttle were okay with spending the money to show you how much a quality detail can do for your car and then do something fun/crazy with the same car, in my opinion, is a testament to the quality they strive for in providing us with some awesome content
